Class AbstractHttpDestination

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.cloudplatform.connectivity.AbstractHttpDestination
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DestinationProperties, HttpDestination, HttpDestinationProperties
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientCredentialsHttpDestination, CustomTokenHttpDestination

    public abstract class AbstractHttpDestination
extends Object
implements HttpDestination
    Abstract implementation of the HttpDestination interface that delegates all interface methods to a base HttpDestinationProperties object.
